# Aggregate Google Analytics data and Email the results

This workflow will check for country views, page engagement and google search console results. It will take this week's data and compare it to last week's data.

[Credit to Keith Rumjahn for the original workflow, which I modified.]({{ $env.WEBHOOK_URL }}

## Property ID

1. Create your [Google Analytics Credentials]({{ $env.WEBHOOK_URL }}
2. Enter your [property ID]({{ $env.WEBHOOK_URL }} or Choose from the List of Properties.

